{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a849c0d9f4","title":"周恩来将陈伯达江青讲话新闻稿送毛泽东批示时附的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"24067c7874","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":2,"articleId":"a849c0d9f4"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3df4ae75e1","name":"干部和干部政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c2db872249","type":"title","text":"周恩来将陈伯达江青讲话新闻稿送毛泽东批示时附的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a849c0d9f4"},{"id":"90e16e8ce3","type":"paragraph","text":"〖十一月二十八日，陈伯达主持《文艺界无产阶级文化大革命大会》。江青在会上讲话，点了彭真、陆定一等人的名。人民日报拟报道此讲话。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a849c0d9f4"},{"id":"9ca1eb7a1e","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a849c0d9f4"},{"id":"78ab1ad18e","type":"paragraph","text":"这一报道，已经中央文革小组通过，并经林彪同志审定，现送主席审批。在第7、9、13页中，有3处指名批判了一些人，是否合适，请主席批示。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a849c0d9f4"},{"id":"ef884c9f5f","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a849c0d9f4"},{"id":"97aa6a458f","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a849c0d9f4"}],"page":{"id":"ea4488d8e1","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a849c0d9f4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}